9 assist with the registration and inspection of registered residential facilities pursuant to Part 1 of
10 Article 1 of Chapter 131D of the General Statutes, as amended by Section 1 of this act; and the
11 sum of eighteen thousand dollars ($18,000) in nonrecurring funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year
12 to purchase equipment, supplies, and other nonrecurring expenses associated with these new
13 positions.
